  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">ZincOx Project</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">- Positive Climate Change Impact: The investment will support recovery of resources and creation of valuable raw materials from hazardous waste. - -Furthermore, unlike the traditional method of zinc recovery, the ZincOx process is energy efficient, environmentaly friendly and has a higher recovery rate, with no resudual waste. - Management of waste: EAFD recovery reduces amount of poisonous waste going to landfills, which is a significant benefit, given a major environmental hazard landfills present for health of population.  - Job Creation and know-how transfer:  Introduction of waste processing on a commercial scale in multiple countries will result on direct and non-direct employment opportunities.  The expansion of the innovative technology will help promote a concept of viable commercial resource-saving and environmentally friendly business model.</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">IFC is investing in ZincOx Resources PLC (ZincOx or the Company), a recent entrant in the zinc recycling sector with an innovative technology, to help it finance pre-operating and research and development expenditures related to potential zinc recycling projects in Turkey, Thailand and Russia.</narrative>
  </description>
